io.dropwizard.validation

Annotation Type ValidationMethod


  • @Target(value={TYPE,ANNOTATION_TYPE,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Constraint(validatedBy=MethodValidator.class)
 @Documented
public @interface ValidationMethod
    Validates a bean predicate method as returning true. Bean predicates must be of the form isSomething or they'll be silently ignored.
